{"tid":2309049,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警稱接報 或再控傳媒查冊","createTime":"2020-12-02T09:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T10:18:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"158b059863e3201544e798b908f87968083a27ed","tid":2309049,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/6BENX4V6QVEJTOWPEWZ5WJGIJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2F6BENX4V6QVEJTOWPEWZ5WJGIJM%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOXza4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=23efe65d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2F6BENX4V6QVEJTOWPEWZ5WJGIJM%2F&h=0a061361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/6BENX4V6QVEJTOWPEWZ5WJGIJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警稱接報 或再控傳媒查冊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oHM5SjUN26DcmnIpqCWoeBbznKk=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DAAJVE6NDBDZXFJYMS6AZUERD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoHM5SjUN26DcmnIpqCWoeBbznKk%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDAAJVE6NDBDZXFJYMS6AZUERD4.jpg&h=fe0d278d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■郭嘉銓昨透露警方再接有關媒體查冊報案。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港台節目《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲因透過查閱車牌資料報道7.21元朗恐襲真相，被警方報復性以涉嫌虛假陳述拘捕。警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓昨在一個網上研討會上透露，蔡玉玲案件是收到「資料擁有人」報案。警方亦接獲其他媒體使用查冊報道的報案，會視乎有否足夠證據作檢控，警方目前正調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指資料擁有人舉報<br />\n<br />\n樹仁大學昨日舉辦「新聞採訪的邊界？」網上研討會，會上郭嘉銓被問到港台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲因查冊被控一案時聲稱，警方是收到資料的擁有人報案，經警方獲取證據，並徵詢律政司意見後，才作拘捕及檢控。換言之，向警方投訴蔡玉玲的，相信就是《7.21誰主真相》提及、7.21當晚接載白衣人及分發竹枝的車輛車主，即元朗區的村代表。<br />\n<br />\n郭嘉銓進一步透露，有收到個別人士。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記協早前已發聲明及向特首發信，要求警方撤銷針對蔡玉玲查冊工作的控罪，「告係好有問題」，促請警方停止針對傳媒查冊的行動。政府應由上而下統一準則，包括容許申請人列明將查冊資料用作新聞用途，讓各政府部門建立清晰的查冊機制，「咁唔需要記者去投訴先拎到資料」。"},{"pid":"ab757dce88a20ad3a7301aadee342688243c020d","tid":2309049,"uid":9328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"今次到蘋果？放心，一定唔會係大公文匯"},{"pid":"ec89b0e750d57cfd19cd7b86f6811733d9b41256","tid":2309049,"uid":143608,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:45:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">換言之，向警方投訴蔡玉玲的，相信就是《7.21誰主真相》提及、7.21當晚接載白衣人及分發竹枝的車輛車主，即元朗區的村代表。</span><br />\n<br />\n白衣人的幫兇仲可以報警拉返你轉頭，警黑合作真係無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8fc6be7a6712847f0689c2a1b00cbefdfb089e","tid":2309049,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"如果記者搵一個普通市民做查冊<br />\n普通市民響香港之外send資料俾記者<br />\n狗查唔查到？"},{"pid":"2cbdbff4ffa71489a5b6d775693d58c9a6f868a2","tid":2309049,"uid":72994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"屌，咁所有被查冊嘅擁有者都可以告人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"057f48f66bc4e4ec8d6e7983c58176d5e485ff14","tid":2309049,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f8fc6be7a6712847f0689c2a1b00cbefdfb089e","tid":2309049,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"如果記者搵一個普通市民做查冊<br />\n普通市民響香港之外send資料俾記者<br />\n狗查唔查到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"查到都做唔到野啦，黑警夠閪膽跨境咬查冊手足咩，而記者只係收到線報"},{"pid":"f70a41ac13d33e511a69b40de047da55559ab134","tid":2309049,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:15:05.000Z","msg":"皇軍玩撚曬"},{"pid":"8e418adc7621c4bfe66afac2cdc02fb1a3904183","tid":2309049,"uid":40415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">揾三個人查冊</span>&gt;<span class=\"gold\">有人匿名提供資料予記者</span>&gt;<span class=\"limegreen\">無法確認資料提供者</span>&gt;<span class=\"teal\">無罪</span><br />\n<span class=\"maroon\">